transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Viagra, can I help you today?

Speaker 2: Yes, hi.

Speaker 1: I just got your pills that you re-sent me out and they're still the generic regular

Speaker 2: Viagra and not the AGV Viagra.

Speaker 1: Got it.

Speaker 2: What does the marking on the pill say on the ones you received?

Speaker 1: Just 100.

Speaker 2: Yeah, that's going to be the marking of the AGV on the pill, sir.

Speaker 1: It only tells you the dosage.

Speaker 2: The wrong one says AC on there, that's the wrong one.

Speaker 1: Right, but they're supposed to, why don't they say AGV?

Speaker 2: They don't say that, that's for marketing reasons only, the only thing you'll see marked

Speaker 1: on there is 100.

Speaker 2: Well, because I'll know real quick, because what I've been told is that if they don't

Speaker 1: say AGV and then 100 on the other side, they're the wrong pill.

Speaker 2: No, they never say AGV on the pill, if you'd like I could transfer you over to the agent

Speaker 1: that you claim said that to you, because I see who you spoke to last.

Speaker 2: No, no, no, nobody said that to me from your office.

Speaker 1: Then where did you get that from then, sir, if it wasn't from the correction?

Speaker 2: From the picture that I see it on, on his four blue advertisement.

Speaker 1: For marketing reasons only, sir.

Speaker 2: The only thing that you'll actually see on the AGV is 100 engraved and that's it.

Speaker 1: And they say it works in 11 minutes, right?

Speaker 2: Yeah, 11 to 15 minutes, the doctor will put an hour on there because he can't confirm

Speaker 1: that everybody's body composition will be the same, so he needs to list that on there.

Speaker 2: Yes, I know that, then why doesn't it say that and then it only says that you're to

Speaker 1: take it an hour before?

Speaker 2: Well, I just explained that right now, the doctor can't confirm that everybody's body

Speaker 1: composition is the same, so he needs to put an hour on there for the general public, but

Speaker 2: these pills do work as fast as 11 to 15 minutes.

Speaker 1: Okay, I will check it out and I will talk to a few other people, then I'll call you

Speaker 2: back if I need to be.

Speaker 1: All right, well, other than that, I hope you have a good one, bye-bye.

Speaker 2: All right, you too.
